30:47.279 --> 30:50.581
I instinctively know
where to press,

30:50.583 --> 30:55.085
Where to squeeze,
where to stroke,

30:55.087 --> 30:56.086
And where to lick.

30:56.088 --> 30:59.556
Won't you let me
show you, lester,

30:59.558 --> 31:03.126
How I can bring
