32:28.280 --> 32:32.749
You know,
teach myself
to disappear

32:32.751 --> 32:33.884
Without ever
going anywhere.

32:33.886 --> 32:36.887
I could be sitting
at the dinner table
and my dad

32:36.889 --> 32:42.192
