33:05.351 --> 33:07.451
To make it look simple.

33:07.453 --> 33:12.389
After a while, I needed
a fearless assistant

33:12.391 --> 33:14.358
To help me pull it off.

33:14.726 --> 33:16.493
And I found

33:16.495 --> 33:18.428
