33:20.031 --> 33:21.331
Brandy.

33:21.333 --> 33:23.133
Sherry.

33:23.267 --> 33:25.068
Scotch.

33:25.570 --> 33:27.337
Bourbon...

33:28.973 --> 33:30.374
Gin.

33:30.376 --> 33:34.211
I always thought
I was just born

33:34.213 --> 33:36.380
With this natural gift.

33:36.382 --> 33:38.615
It wasn't until
I quit drinking,

33:38.617 --> 33:44.021
Until my sobriety
allowed me this, uh...

33:47.959 --> 33:49.993
Magnificent

33:50.962 --> 33:54.765
Clarity that
I realized...

33:56.000 --> 33:59.136
I'd had a teacher
all along.

33:59.704 --> 34:01.171
My dad...

34:01.173 --> 34:03.440
The greatest magician
