he wouldn't let me
get in the car.

34:27.066 --> 34:28.598
He'd make me walk home,

34:28.600 --> 34:31.234
Once in, uh,
once in a heat wave,

34:31.236 --> 34:34.171
Once in a snowstorm.

34:35.073 --> 34:38.442
