get smaller and smaller

34:42.714 --> 34:46.683
As he drove into
the distance until...

34:47.051 --> 34:49.953
Poof. He was gone.

34:52.423 --> 34:57.227
Without saying a word,
just by his example,

34:57.295 --> 35:01.598
