38:42.020 --> 38:45.021
And in the meantime,
he'd be trying to
make me laugh,

38:45.023 --> 38:46.790
Doing all these
crazy routines,

38:46.792 --> 38:48.958
Most of which he just
stole off the tv.

38:48.960 --> 38:51.461
One day he knocked
on the door and
my sister answered it,

38:51.463 --> 38:55.832
All smiles
and batted eyelashes,
"oh, francis."

38:55.834 --> 38:58.601
And he said,
"actually, leona,

38:58.603 --> 39:00.570
"I'm here for pauline."

39:00.572 --> 39:02.272
(chuckles)

39:03.040 --> 39:06.176
So how about you
and bill?

39:06.377 --> 39:08.378
Oh, um, uh,

39:08.380 --> 39:11.781
