what I missed, really.

39:48.053 --> 39:52.455
Things I just chalked up
to his having
a big personality.

39:52.457 --> 39:56.826
But, god,
the mood swings,

39:57.461 --> 39:58.995
The impulsivity...

39:58.997 --> 40:04.567
A new car, a new house,
a new medical partnership.

40:05.102 --> 40:07.470
