recognize the person
I was before.

40:53.552 --> 40:56.386
I was the
go-along gal,

40:56.720 --> 40:59.022
The laugh you could
always count on.

40:59.024 --> 41:04.093
I didn't wanna make waves,
didn't ever wanna
upset anyone.

41:04.929 --> 41:07.096
Mmm, I tell ya,
it felt good to do
something

41:07.098 --> 41:10.066
