He just...

43:21.932 --> 43:24.067
He reminded me.

43:26.036 --> 43:29.539
I forgot that there

43:29.541 --> 43:31.774
Were these triplets
that moved in

43:31.776 --> 43:32.942
Across the street from us
that summer.

43:32.944 --> 43:37.647
And every morning
he wanted to go off
with them.

43:38.983 --> 43:42.118
And I wanted him
to stay home,

43:42.753 --> 43:44.687
Play with me.

43:45.222 --> 43:47.190
Just with me.

43:48.626 --> 43:50.259
And so...

43:50.594 --> 43:56.065
I invented this game
to keep him interested.

43:59.303 --> 44:01.871
(whispers)
and it worked.

44:02.039 --> 44:04.774
You don't know that
that's what happened.

44:04.776 --> 44:07.176
It makes sense,
virginia.

44:07.178 --> 44:11.214
If he had violated me,
how could we be so close?

44:13.050 --> 44:14.651
How could I want
to see him be happy?

44:14.653 --> 44:16.719
Barb, these things
are complicated.

44:16.721 --> 44:20.657
