50:55.185 --> 50:57.019
You saw it
happen to me.

50:58.688 --> 51:00.122
What makes you think
the same thing

51:00.124 --> 51:01.390
Didn't happen to me
after you were gone?

51:01.392 --> 51:03.793
That I was
your replacement?

51:05.729 --> 51:10.066
Because if I thought
that was possible, I...

51:11.101 --> 51:14.537
I never would've
left you behind.

51:16.473 --> 51:19.842
No, you,
you were the apple
of his eye.

51:20.310 --> 51:22.178
He'd show you off
in front of company,

51:22.180 --> 51:25.748
Make you perform.
For christ's sake,
he gave you his name.

51:25.750 --> 51:27.850
What father skips over
his firstborn

51:27.852 --> 51:29.852
To give his second son
his name?

51:29.854 --> 51:32.421
A son of a bitch,
