51:40.498 --> 51:42.631
Look, whatever
you need to believe
to keep yourself

51:42.633 --> 51:45.868
On the straight
and narrow.

51:47.070 --> 51:49.405
I'm healed, bill.

51:49.673 --> 51:52.174
That's what
the truth does.

51:52.176 --> 51:54.910
You just have to be
