52:15.533 --> 52:17.032
He left you,

52:17.434 --> 52:19.568
And you left me.

52:22.239 --> 52:24.507
I don't blame you
for it.

52:25.475 --> 52:27.009
I did.

52:29.246 --> 52:31.680
But I understand now.

52:33.216 --> 52:35.451
And I forgive you.

52:44.561 --> 52:47.229
(indistinct conversations)

52:47.231 --> 52:50.065
(telephone ringing
in distance)

52:55.906 --> 52:58.174
Robert: We got heat out
