53:30.140 --> 53:33.809
We need someone
to make a sandwich run.

53:49.092 --> 53:51.660
What can I get for you?

53:52.362 --> 53:53.996
I'm fine.

53:54.397 --> 53:56.031
Really?
(bottle thuds)

53:56.033 --> 53:57.299
Nothing, huh?

53:57.301 --> 54:00.769
