what you mean.

54:13.984 --> 54:15.651
Does drinking

54:15.653 --> 54:18.787
Help to relieve
your conscience about

54:18.789 --> 54:23.058
What it is
we're doing here
with each other?

54:23.060 --> 54:25.761
About what it is we're...

54:25.895 --> 54:28.163
We are doing to libby?

54:28.765 --> 54:30.232
Libby?

54:31.635 --> 54:35.204
(scoffs) where is
