56:02.560 --> 56:07.229
You can poke at it
and prod it,
but you cannot change it.

56:08.164 --> 56:09.832
So you move on.

56:10.233 --> 56:12.835
You do your best,
which is what I've done.

56:12.837 --> 56:14.770
